  Trey Gowdy said he wants Hillary Clinton to testify in public about her use of a private email server . 
  The former Secretary of State will testify the week of May 18 and again before June 18 about the 2012 terror attacks in Benghazi . 
  The September 11, 2012 attacks killed four Americans including the US ambassador to Libya . 
  The first hearing will focus on Clinton's use of private emails and the second on the Benghazi attacks . 
  Clinton will be the first to testify about the attacks in public . 
  She has refused to answer questions about her handling of the attacks . 
 